The $\mathrm{SU}_2$-TQFT $\boV_p$ corresponds in Conformal Field Theory to the Wess-Zumino-Witten model at odd level $\ell=p-2$. Similar $\mathrm{SU}_2$-TQFTs exist at  even levels, that is, when $p$ is even. Their signature functions can again be computed using the Frobenius algebra formalism of Theorem~\ref{DM1}.  But we won't consider even level $\mathrm{SU}_2$-TQFTs in this paper.
