 (-1)^{\lfloor {jq}/{p}\rfloor +\lfloor {kq}/{p}\rfloor+\lfloor {\ell q}/{p}\rfloor}
\end{equation}
to transform this expression into a sum of evaluations of a rational function at roots of unity indexed by $\Delta_p$.

