For part (b), the text gives a proof idea in genus zero: using the closed formula \eqref{eq:genus0}
\[
\langle \tau_{e_1} \cdots \tau_{e_n} \rangle_0 = \frac{(n-3)!}{e_1! \cdots e_n!},
\]
