D : E(n, 3g-3+n) \to \QQ, \qquad D(\ee) = \int_{\Mbar_{g,n}} \psi_1^{e_1} \cdots \psi_n^{e_n}
\]
satisfies conditions \textup{(S)}, \textup{(LC)}, and \textup{(P)} of Theorem~\ref{thm:main_theorem_paper}.
