\t\begin{align*}
int_{G_{\rho}^\la(z_0)}H(z,|\na u|)\,dz
int_{G_{2\rho}^\la(z_0)}H(z,|F|) \,dz\,.
\t\end{align*}\t
\end{lemma}

This separation “is effective in the presence of $F$ under the sharp range of phase parameters
\begin{align} \label{range_pq}
2\le p <\infty, \quad p<q\le p+\alpha\,.    
